      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="1c06-5502-fb5a-616e">When this Unit is nominated to deploy from the Reserves, it may resolve the PLACE (18) effect from the controlling player&apos;s Entry Edge. No model may be set Within 10&quot; of any Enemy model. This Unit&apos;s Activation ends.</characteristic>
